	  <concept id="i1075151"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">42.705</ph> Final indirect cost rates.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d2498e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2509e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Final indirect cost rates shall be established on the basis of-</p>
					          <ol id="d2498e23" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2509e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Contracting officer determination procedure (see <xref href="FAR-i1075175.dita#i1075175"
                              base="i1075175"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">42.705-1</xref>), or</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2509e39" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Auditor determination procedure (see <xref href="FAR-i1075238.dita#i1075238"
                              base="i1075238"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">42.705-2</xref>).</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2509e53" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Within 120 days (or longer period, if approved in writing by the contracting officer,) after settlement of the final annual indirect cost rates for all years of a physically complete contract, the contractor must submit a completion invoice or voucher reflecting the settled amounts and rates. To determine whether a period longer than 120 days is appropriate, the contracting officer should consider whether there are extenuating circumstances, such as the following:</p>
					          <ol id="d2498e59" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2509e63" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Pending closeout of subcontracts awaiting Government audit.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2509e72" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Pending contractor, subcontractor, or Government claims.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2509e81" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Delays in the disposition of Government property.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2509e90" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Delays in contract reconciliation.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2509e99" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(5)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Any other pertinent factors.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2509e110" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            
					          </p>
					          <ol id="d2498e116" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2509e120" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                If the contractor fails to submit a completion invoice or voucher within the time specified in paragraph (b) of this section, the contracting officer may-</p>
							              <ol id="d2498e126" class="- topic/ol ">
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d2509e130" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Determine the amounts due to the contractor under the contract; and</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d2509e139" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Record this determination in a unilateral modification to the contract.</p>
								                </li>
							              </ol>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2509e150" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                This contracting officer determination must be issued as a final decision in accordance with <xref href="FAR-i1080268.dita#i1080268"
                              base="i1080268"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">33.211</xref>.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
